```class Solution {
    public long minimumCost(String s) {
        long res = 0;
        int ones = 0, zeros = 0;
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            if (c == '0') zeros++;
            else ones++;
        }
        res += Math.min(ones, zeros);
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length() - 1; i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) != s.charAt(i + 1)) {
                res += Math.min(i + 1, s.length() - i - 1);
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
